data.description: Seller will consider a buy down on your interest rate with acceptable offer. Welcome HOME to the postcard community of The Ponds!  With it's Southern Charm,  enchantment and resort style amenities, The Ponds and 105 Loon Drive boasts everything you could ever want in a home and community!  With its expertly designed floor plan of five large bedrooms, with the Primary bedroom being on the main level, three and half baths and arguably one of the largest lofts of any floor plan in The Ponds,, look no further for your future home.  The Tillman Floorplan features a formal dining room adjoining to the kitchen and great room which leads out to a large screened in patio and your private backyard with protected wetlands behind it.  Upstairs you'll find four additional large bedrooms, two full bathrooms, the laundry room and the versatile large loft/flex space. Upstairs you'll find four additional large bedrooms, two full bathrooms, the laundry room and the versatile large loft/flex space.  This golf cart friendly community offers it's residents endless opportunities for leisure activities; community pool, playground area, YMCA, amphitheater, dog park, fire station, endless trails for walking or biking and a beautiful clubhouse and its all within the highly sought out DD2 School District.  Schedule your showing TODAY and make this large gorgeous Charleston style home yours just in time for the Holidays!
